{"tid":1616373,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你班柒頭,係想救香港既同我入黎填撚左佢.記得在 email 裏 click confirm!!","createTime":"2019-10-03T11:49:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T04:18:15.000Z","uid":221203,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"799a45291803d60bcd2e9203001018e31fee22e6","tid":1616373,"uid":221203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:49:08.000Z","msg":"《美國白宮聯署》<br />\n<br />\n差佬已經開真槍謀殺，我哋真係急需救援！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">簽完後，記得在 email 裏 click confirm！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 請求美國行使《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法》，制裁侵犯人權的香港官員或知名人士。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2mIGUn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2mIGUn2&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEhSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=64f7a3f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2mIGUn2</a><br />\n尚欠 19000 人聯署，10 月 10 日截止。<br />\n<br />\n2. 請求美國通過《香港保護法案》，暫停向香港警察出售催淚彈、胡椒噴霧、橡膠子彈和其他防暴物品。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2m39jUJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2m39jUJ&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEhSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=afe2ebc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2m39jUJ</a><br />\n尚欠 53000 人聯署，10 月 14 日截止。<br />\n<br />\n3. 請求美國將香港警察加入《香港人權及民主法案》的制裁名單。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kyBsT1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kyBsT1&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEhSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=c4a81323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kyBsT1</a><br />\n尚欠 58000 人聯署，10 月 16 日截止。<br />\n<br />\n4. 請求美國承認香港為美國保護區。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kK8y2q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kK8y2q&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEhSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=734cb420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kK8y2q</a><br />\n尚欠 55000 人聯署，10 月 20 日截止。"},{"pid":"027ec55ddb8f4ee0f26cb6c80e07e0cfaae2f47b","tid":1616373,"uid":221203,"like":0,"disl